title: New leveling system
body: Just a question, do i get the rewards from level 1-30 if I'm already level 30 once the patch is launched?

replies.body:
TLDR; No =\

It sounds a lot worse than it actually is though!!! You can check out all the little details over on our [**Preseason Update FAQ**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/115012640908-Preseason-Update-FAQ), but here's the part you need right now ^_^
